::Magmatron/Bobertron::

    Bobertron walked back into the lab room. He noticed that a small insect 
was crawling toward the ventilation shaft. He went to crush it when Magmatron 
put his hand out.
    "Crush that bug and end your life," Magmatron said to Bobertron. "What 
happened to CyberShark?"
    "He went to help the Maximals in the battles against the Predacons," 
Bobertron said. "He hasn't returned yet, nor has he commed in to report. I 
think he may be offline."
    "Well, then you are wrong, I sense him now, on the verge of something 
big," Magmatron said. "CyberShark, return to base at once, I have important 
business to discuss with you."
